title: SC EP:782 I Did Not Think It Was Real
itunes:title: SC EP:782 I Did Not Think It Was Real
description: Tonight we will be speaking to Patrick who comes to us from Louisiana. Patrick has been hunting his whole life and grew up thinking Sasquatch was nonsense, made up bedtime stories for people to tell their kids. In 2003, he was hunting and was chased out of an area by a female creature. Patrick said “I could not believe what I was seeing.”
